{"tid":2319161,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港電台：彭黛玲晤羅冠聰　英方粗暴干涉中國內政和香港事務","createTime":"2020-12-10T01:54:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T05:31:28.000Z","uid":290404,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3c998423c402ce1611b092eac38d58e2efcd85b1","tid":2319161,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T01:54:32.000Z","msg":"英國內政大臣彭黛玲，在倫敦與前香港眾志常委羅冠聰會面。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>中方曾經批評，英方為有關人員在英居留及入籍提供路徑，公然違背自身承諾，粗暴干涉中國內政和香港事務，嚴重違反國際法和國際關係基本準則。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564506-20201210.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564506-20201210.htm&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYpgPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=f1d8a619\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564506-20201210.htm&h=efa36922\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564506-20201210.htm</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fdf3bd42eb2966f5f58831dac0fc0436c81c4aa","tid":2319161,"uid":290404,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T01:58:18.000Z","msg":"英國內政大臣彭黛玲與身在倫敦的前香港眾志主席羅冠聰會面。彭黛玲表示，對北京決定引入港區國安法深表遺憾，有關做法嚴重破壞中英聯合聲明，又指今次的會面非常有價值，會尋求盡可能對港人提供協助。彭黛玲之後發表聲明，承諾會與港人一起，並恪守承諾，支持及悍衛港人自由。羅冠聰就指，可以與主導BNO計劃的彭黛玲會面是寶貴的機會，他感謝英國政府在關鍵時刻提供了BNO計劃，令部分港人免受政治打壓，日後會爭取與更多英國內閣官員會面，促使國際更了解中共的威權擴強。 今次有份見彭黛玲的，<strong>還包括<span class=\"red\">涉嫌偷越邊境被扣留深圳的「香港故事」成員李宇軒</span>的妹妹</strong>。她在會面上感謝彭黛玲，又希望英國繼續為生活方式被徹底催毀的香港人做多一點事。安排今次會面的倫敦市長保守黨候選人貝利表示，對香港年輕人爭取權利和自由的勇氣印象深刻，希望港人知道，倫敦會熱烈歡迎香港人的到來。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2370021\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2370021&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYpgPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=5ef93700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2370021</a>"},{"pid":"9b12560b1db11225c8aa971f35f77bad35e86443","tid":2319161,"uid":78971,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T01:58:38.000Z","msg":"羅生係叛國賊吖嘛？<br />\n咁佢見咩人關你中國咩事<br />\n<br />\n做人拎得起放得低啦<br />\n全天候怨婦咁<br />\n大家冇晒關係，見咩人講咩嘢，關你咩事呢？"},{"pid":"c503fb1309ec920f829e832c22da07edb0e6e552","tid":2319161,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T02:02:44.000Z","msg":"三萬黑警飛去英國拉羅冠聰未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d97c6973bfeb95c7b8b891f011c7d8d46b5ed889","tid":2319161,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T02:04:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68aba8b95e48b35467ebb75ceafe490a6933ad9b","tid":2319161,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T02:04:41.000Z","msg":"快D叫李桂華出擊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e31e919d6fd08e21869c488aa73349959ce25446","tid":2319161,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T02:04:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52ec51e7e68a49d347e661013da78d78deec8c27","tid":2319161,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T02:05:44.000Z","msg":"支那狗想見人地唔so佢？"},{"pid":"28455f0ee2e027ff932b4284e1413f7566682a14","tid":2319161,"uid":90601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T02:07:12.000Z","msg":"香港人：存在<br />\n外國人：Hi, Hong Konger<br />\n中國：粗暴干涉中國內政和香港事務！！"},{"pid":"36c05df65c